snippet.title: abzcorner角有角忙
snippet.description:
Hello! 這是一個用來分享日常繪圖與設計的頻道。歡迎訂閱、按讚與分享。
歡迎拜訪我的部落格：https://abzcorner.blogspot.com/
其他合作email 與我聯絡：abzcorner@gmail.com

abzcorner頻道非作為商業用途，如果有問題請告知，以做出後續處理。
希望這個頻道能為你帶來生活上的一點點娛樂! Enjoy~

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Hello! This is a channel about the process of my illustration and design. 
Welcome to share, like and follow.

I have been in graphic design industry for over 10 years, I would like to share my experience by this platform.
All videos are non-business using, feel free to comment.

Hope this channel can bring you a little fun in life, enjoy!
Welcome if any cooperation or question, email: abzcorner@gmail.com
